### Session Service (`app/services/session_service.py`)

#### [MODIFY] [session_service.py](file:///d:/Project/Current/Final_Year_Project/Interview_with_AI/app/services/session_service.py)
- Refactor `create_session` to accept optional `group_id`, `group_name`, `project_template`, `start_at`, `end_at`, `candidate_email` and persist them
- Add `create_sessions_bulk(request: BulkSessionCreateRequest) → BulkSessionCreateResponse`:
  - Validate: group_name, start_at < end_at, end_at > now, duration in [15, 180], template required, email format, no duplicate emails/names, ≤20 rows
  - If dry_run=True: return per-row validation status only (no DB write, no email)
  - If dry_run=False: loop candidates, create sessions, send emails, persist group summary to `session_groups` collection, return per-row status
  - `group_id` format: `group_{timestamp}_{6hex}`
- Add window enforcement in `get_session` and `start_session`: if `start_at` and `now < start_at` → raise `WindowNotStartedError`; if `end_at` and `now > end_at` → raise `WindowExpiredError` (caller turns these into 403)
- Add `get_session_groups(limit=20) → List[SessionGroupSummary]`: queries `session_groups` collection sorted by `created_at` desc

